OL,3,CPrestigious all-girls island school
OL,4,Cresponds to cyber attack
OL,6,FThe Ladies' College in Guernsey has
OL,7,Fbeen asked to improve its security
OL,8,Fmeasures following a cyber attack in
OL,9,FJune last year.
OL,11,FA report published by the island's
OL,12,Fregulatory authority, the Office of
OL,13,Fthe Data Protection Authority (ODPA),
OL,14,Ffound that "failures in The Ladies'
OL,15,FCollege's security allowed for
OL,16,Funauthorised access to be gained to
OL,17,Fits systems".
