OL,6,FThey added that the school notified
OL,7,Fthe ODPA of the breach at the time of
OL,8,Fthe incident.
OL,10,F"We reacted quicklyto launch an
OL,11,Finvestigation into the incident and
OL,12,Feffectively managed the incident
OL,13,Fwithout any disruption to teaching,"
OL,14,Fthe college stated.
