OL,3,CPrestigious all-girls island school
OL,4,Cresponds to cyber attack
OL,6,F"The Ladies' College takes data
OL,7,Fsecurity very seriously; we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to protecting the personal
OL,9,Finformation of our students, parents
OL,10,Fand staff, and are grateful for the
OL,11,Fsupport of the ODPA throughout this
OL,12,Fprocess."
OL,14,FThe ODPA said the College was
OL,15,F"vulnerable to a brute force attack"
OL,16,Fdue to a combination of factors,
OL,17,Fincluding a weak password, failure to
OL,18,Fset up Multi-Factor Authentication,
OL,19,Fand failure to secure an administrator
OL,20,Faccount.
