OL,6,FIt also found the College had not
OL,7,Fproperly secured remote access to
OL,8,Fcomputers within its network.
OL,10,FThe ODPA's Data Protection
OL,11,FCommissioner, Brent Homan, said:
OL,12,F"Effective processes to monitor and
OL,13,Fwarn against security breaches are a
OL,14,Fkey element of any security safeguard
OL,15,Fsystem, regardless of the sensitivity
OL,16,Fof the information held.
