OL,6,F"We are pleased that the Ladies
OL,7,FCollege acted swiftly to notify our
OL,8,Foffice of the breach, cooperated with
OL,9,Fthe investigation and implemented
OL,10,Fremedial measures without delay."
OL,12,FThe Ladies' College said it
OL,13,F"cooperated fully with the ODPA's
OL,14,Finvestigations" and has since
OL,15,F"implemented a range of measures" to
OL,16,Fenhance the security of its IT systems.
